{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSTextArea","symbolKind":"struct","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTextArea"}],"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSTextAreaV","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTextArea","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Text area is a UI element that allows to type, edit, or select longer blocks of textual data, such as comments, messages or descriptions;","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by expanding vertically and offering more space to input text.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It provides a visual and interactive affordance for multiline text entry while supporting labels, placeholders, descriptions, and validation feedback.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Structures","anchor":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/Helperlink"],"generated":true},{"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/init(_:tableName:bundle:text:placeholder:helperText:helperLink:isOutlined:constrainedMaxWidth:status:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/init(label:text:placeholder:helperText:helperLink:isOutlined:constrainedMaxWidth:status:)"],"generated":true},{"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/body"],"generated":true},{"title":"Enumerations","anchor":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/HelperText","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/Status"],"generated":true},{"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTextArea","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"text":"Layout","type":"heading","anchor":"Layout","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text area is based on several configurable UI elements:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"label","type":"text"}]},{"text":": It is used to describe the purpose of the text area.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In some UI contexts, especially when space is limited or when the text area is part of a compact layout, the label can be hidden.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, hiding the label should only be done if the purpose remains clear thanks to a placeholder or contextual icon","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and if the label is still accessible to screen readers.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Hiding a label is a design choice that must balance visual simplicity and clarity of intent, without compromising inclusiveness or form guidance.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"placeholder","type":"text"}]},{"text":": If the text of the text area is empty a placeholder provides a hint or guidance inside the field to suggest expected input.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Status","type":"heading","anchor":"Status","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Five status are proposed for all layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"enabled (by default)","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Default neutral appearance, whether empty or filled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It allows users to click, focus, and type freely without restrictions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"error","type":"text"}]},{"text":": The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"text":" status indicates that the user input does not meet validation rules or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"expected formatting. It provides immediate visual feedback, typically through a red border,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"an error icon, and a clear, accessible error message positioned below the text area. The error message replaces the helper text.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"loading","type":"text"}]},{"text":": The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"loading"},{"text":" state indicates that the system is processing or retrieving data","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"related to the text entered. A progress indicator appears to inform the user that an action is in progress.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The field remains editable while loading.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"readOnly","type":"text"}]},{"text":": The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readOnly"},{"text":" status lets the text visible but not editable.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"disabled","type":"text"}]},{"text":": In ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"disabled"},{"text":" status, the field is non-interactive and grayed out to indicate it cannot be changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note the SwiftUI ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View.disabled()"},{"text":" is ignored.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Helpers","type":"heading","anchor":"Helpers","level":2},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helper text (plain)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A supporting text conveys additional information about the text area,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as how it will be used. It should ideally only take up a single line, though may wrap"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to multiple lines if required, and be either persistently visible or visible only on focus."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helper text (characters max count)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Uses an internal message displaying the count of remaining characters depending to the given value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is a specific iOS library feature with 1.4.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helper link","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": If the helper text is not sufficient, it’s possible to offer the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an additional help link (the link can be external or open a modal)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default no haptics are done by the component.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However you should think about cases where you will have to make the devices vibrate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can refer to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/design\/human-interface-guidelines\/playing-haptics","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Mandatory field indication","type":"heading","anchor":"Mandatory-field-indication","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If all fields are mandatory (several fields present): display the message “All fields are mandatory” at the top of your formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Do not use an asterisk at the end of each field label, nor the word “mandatory.”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If not all fields are mandatory (several fields present): display the message “All fields marked with an * are mandatory” at the top of your formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use an asterisk (*) at the end of each mandatory field label, and ensures this is well vocalized.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"UI rendering of the asterisk must be done with ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bold font weight"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative content color"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" (red on light backgrounds).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use the mention “(optional)” at the end of each optional field label. Note that this rule is not systematic, it remains an option, to be used if needed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is only one field in the formular, or if the mandatory nature is obvious,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"no mention is necessary since the fields are essential to the formular’s functionality.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Outlined style","type":"heading","anchor":"Outlined-style","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":", the text area uses a subtle background fill and a bottom border only, creating a softer and more contained look.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"outlined"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":", the text area uses a transparent background and a visible stroke on all four sides.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This style may be appropriate for contexts where inputs need to feel lightweight and unobtrusive,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for example inside a card, a dialog, or a filtering panel.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ An outlined text area","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text, isOutlined: true)"]},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ The text to display and edit","    @State var text: String = \"\"","","    \/\/ Empty text and no placeholder","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text)","","    \/\/ Empty text with placeholder","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text, placeholder: \"Describe your issue in detail\")","","    \/\/ With a plain helper text","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\",","                 text: $text,","                 placeholder: \"Describe your issue in detail\",","                 helperText: .plain(\"Maximum 500 characters.\"))","","    \/\/ With a maximum character count — the component shows \"X characters remaining\" (bold)","    \/\/ and switches to an error style when exceeded.","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\",","                 text: $text,","                 helperText: .charactersMaxCount(500))","","    \/\/ With helper link","    @Environment(\\.openURL) private var openUrl","","    let helperLink = OUDSTextArea.Helperlink(text: \"Helper Link\") {","       openUrl.callAsFunction(url)","    }","","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text, placeholder: \"Placeholder\", helperLink: helperLink)","","    \/\/ With error status","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text, status: .error(message: \"This field can't be empty.\"))","","    \/\/ Outlined style","    OUDSTextArea(label: \"Comments\", text: $text, isOutlined: true)"]},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-text-area","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_textArea_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_textArea_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_textArea_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_textArea_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstextarea"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"component_textArea_Orange":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_textArea_Orange.png"}],"alt":"A text area component in light and dark modes with Orange theme","type":"image","identifier":"component_textArea_Orange"},"https://r.orange.fr/r/S-ouds-doc-text-area":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-text-area","title":"unified-design-system.orange.com","url":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-text-area"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTextArea/Status":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstextarea\/status","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Define all available status for the text area"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTextArea\/Status","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Status"}],"title":"OUDSTextArea.Status","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Status"}],"rol